The purpose of this project is to automate the data collection by surveyors who go to different locations to capture details like wind speed, air density, humidity, etc. in order to set up power plants. This application deals with installation of 3 types of power plants - wind, solar and tidal. The result is to generate a list of most suitable locations for installing power plants.
